##Add & Modify to the file (caution: for my own use)
####Look for others.xml or cscfeature.xml. CSC

Change Signal Bar:-
<CscFeature_SystemUI_ConfigOpBrandingForDataIndicator>[B][U]ATT[/U][/B]</CscFeature_SystemUI_ConfigOpBrandingForDataIndicator>
<CscFeature_SystemUI_ConfigOpBrandingForIndicatorIcon>[B][U]ATT[/U][/B]</CscFeature_SystemUI_ConfigOpBrandingForIndicatorIcon>
<CscFeature_SystemUI_ConfigOverrideDataIcon>LTE</CscFeature_SystemUI_ConfigOverrideDataIcon>
<CscFeature_SystemUI_ConfigOpBrandingForIndicatorIcon>LTE</CscFeature_SystemUI_ConfigOpBrandingForIndicatorIcon>

4G=4G
LTE=LTE
ATT=AT&T
VZW=Verizon
TMB=Tmobile
TMK=MetroPCS
USC=U.S. Cellular
XAS=Samsung Unbranded Sprint
SPR=Sprint

Add NFC Icon on Status Bar:-
<CscFeature_NFC_StatusBarIconType>ATT</CscFeature_NFC_StatusBarIconType>
or
<CscFeature_NFC_StatusBarIconType>TRUE</CscFeature_NFC_StatusBarIconType>

Requirements:
-DEVICE MUST BE ROOTED (KNOX=0x1)
-SAMSUNG DEVICE RUNNING ANDROID 5 OR ABOVE (Maybe older versions might work)
-A File Manager that Allows you to Modify device's root directory

Steps:
1. Apply the lines
2. Reboot or restart SystemUI
